Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:14.00,x3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(505,44)}Preložil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:14.00,x3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(329,42)}Korekcia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Saphirro,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(555,75)}Saphirro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Saphirro,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(397,77)}Minako-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, krásna ruža sa chystá kvitnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:18.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje lístky prekypujú červenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje listy pružné a zelené.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:24.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoja lesklá, vlhká vôňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:32.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Príjmi moju krv tvojimi perami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:36.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochutnaj jazykom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:41.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhas smäd predtým než umrieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo robí?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno pantomímu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Recituje básne počas bitky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:15.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorí, že ľudstvo, ktoré zabudne na poéziu, je odsúdene k zániku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:19.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ja som stratil múzu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:22.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a moje básne ostávajú nedokončené...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:33.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V 1. dni na svete, pod stromom života,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:40.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}dvaja z nás počuli hlasy veľrýb, odrážajúce sa z diaľky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:46.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}So všetkým, čo sme stratili a všetko, čo sme milovali,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:53.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}čo sme mali v náručí, kam sa to zatúľalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:59.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Odpoveď leží v jantári slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:05.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Ak by som ťa nestretla, zničila by som anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:11.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Moja duša posadnutá okamihom nesmrteľnosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:15.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}nezraní moje krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:21.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Zrodila som sa, aby som spoznala tento pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:28.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 1.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, som ťa ľúbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:34.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 8.000 rokoch, som ťa ľúbila ešte viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:40.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po ďalších 100.000.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, ťa budem stále ľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:49.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Od 1. dňa, keď som ťa spoznala, hudba v mojom pekle nikdy neprestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Napíšte správu o "Kameni sily," povedali...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:03.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1500)\pos(310,214)}"Rytier keramínovej ruže"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A nemôžeme použiť internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to máme nájsť
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,v tomto obrovskom množstve vedomostí?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesranduješ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:12.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to krásna kniha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:18.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to Lithica, kniha šperkov.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je pripisovaná Onomakrite Grécka,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ale tiež ju volajú Básne Orpheusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš veľa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Orpheus učil o nesmrteľnosti duše.\N Píše sa tu, že ju napísali v Alisii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Orpheus učil o nesmrteľnosti duše.\N Musím to ukázať bratovy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:37.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Duša je nesmrteľná a pohybuje sa z tela na telo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Inými slovami, nikdy nekončiaci kruh reinkarnácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šperky sú tiež elementy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:46.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,rovnako ako ľudia majú takzvaný klenot ich duše v nich...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebola Rena knihovníčka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(Anémia = chudokrvnosť)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále je v posteli s anémiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som tu na jej mieste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto kniha je len orientačná a nemožno ju požičať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, chápem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia, počkaj na mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Len minútku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaujímalo by ma, prečo je tak rozrušená?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňte ma,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:38.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,hľadám knihu Lithica, napísanú Alisiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruža...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak tu je jeden bez krídel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:59.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ktorý rozumie kráse zničenia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:04.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To môže byť tým, že tento bez krídel je nešťastie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Taká silná rezonácia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je jedno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukážem ti pravú krásu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:25.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi. Toto je pre teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je obmedzená?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:32.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šľachta si ju môže požičiať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ušla mi výnimka z pravidiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nebolo fér pre Silviu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:45.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Princezná sleduje Toma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty psisko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolelo... amazonka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:59.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto sú Kronenburg Alisias, zobralo mi to veľa úsilia aby vyrástli...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Za to sa ospravedlňujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale vidíš, tu ešte nejaké ostali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úbohé zvyšky nie sú hodné
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,aby sa stáli kráľovnami kvetov!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ale cítim k nim ľútosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy ľudia nerozumiete
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,aké je to žiť v ponížení!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:27.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasné, ako šlachtická rodina Alisie biedne žije...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ticho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:32.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebuď tak namyslený len preto,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,že ľudia hovoria, že si Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:38.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je toto? Je to princ žiarlivý?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si povedal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slnečné Krídlo" je hlúpy mýtus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš to teraz vyriešiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:54.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat je skutočné Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je s ňou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neboj sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš trpieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo do-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:14.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem... sa k ním ani priblížiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:43.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V nádeji, môžu naše modlitby odpovedať, dám ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:47.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zober si tento šperk do rúk, žiarivý ako lúče slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:53.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako transparentné vody z prameňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šperk, ktorý uchováva plamene
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:02.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,šľahajúce z nesmrteľného slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:07.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vzdialená a nesmrteľná duša sa veselí v nesmrteľných plameňoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:13.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dones to do chrámu a nik neodmietne tvoje modlitby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:18.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Alebo ho nos zo sebou na cestách plných tŕňov.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:27.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V koho tele duša, ktorá napísala túto báseň, je teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je tu nič ako reinkarnácia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezmysel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:58.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už 3 mestá boli totožne zničené.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zničenie je úplné.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:05.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy predtým sme nevideli takéto úplné zničenie stavieb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:09.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Analytici Deavy sa domnievajú...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:15.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...že je tu 67% šanca, že ďalší cieľ bude Alabama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto predpoveď je nepresná.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to skôr Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri sa na toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:51.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto sú analýzy údajov zo zničených oblastí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďalej je pohľad na každé, z rôznych uhlov.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevidíš to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto je ďalší Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:04.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepriateľ sa snaží označiť dokonalý päťuholník.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je absurdné.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvrdíš, že poznáš plány Ťieňových anjelov?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To neviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale chápem krásu geometrických tvarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odmietaš závery tímu expertov
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:23.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,na základe takéhoto uvažovania?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:27.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Pretože v stávke sú životy mnohých.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo to tak spracoval?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystické beštie sa objavili v Memphise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:41.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ako predpovedal Sirius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:41.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvládol si to, Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri! Lúč svetla!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:07.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci elementi, pripraviť na útok!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerozkazuj mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za svetlo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:22.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič optické nereaguje!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Naše srdcia cítia svetlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale svetlo je...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,krásne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:29.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci elementi pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachytili sme neobvyklé vzorce mozgových vĺn talamus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krásne...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:41.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevedel som, že mýtické beštie vedia vyžarovať také krásne svetlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako som tušil, žiadny znak sa neobjavil na tvojom chrbte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:52.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak potom toto dieťa nie je Slnečné Krídlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:53.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:58.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obnovenie kráľovstva Alisie skončí ako sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:03.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia si pamätá jej minulý život, ale ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríš, že tento chlapec je Slnečné Krídlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je jedno, vie pilotovať Aquariona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastavte to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie... Silvie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:24.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie, je čas na šermiarsku skúšku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:28.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz nemám čas sa s tebou hrať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat... Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:34.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa so mnou nezahráš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakramentsky jasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zelenáč ako ty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potrebuje transplantáciu charakteru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to proste kríženec, po tom všetkom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,nemôže zachrániť Barona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som hlava. Za mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmĺkni!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:14.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak toto je sila tajnej geometrickej štruktúry Antichthonu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krása ma silu na to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,aby sa ti dokonca aj bezkrídli klaňali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:27.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Antichthon odstráni ich ohavnosť a dá nam silu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepnúť na Bindu kameru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké perfekné dodecahedrony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, oni sú perfektné decahedrony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem potvrdiť iba 10 úrovňové plochy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:45.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Deformujú priestor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Deformujú naše vedomie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Viac dimenzionálne geografické vzory mýtických beštií
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ovplyvňujú naše myšlienky v mozgoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie je to nádherné, nemyslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:00.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krása je ohavná; ohavnosť je krásna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aká hnusná aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš byť Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že neveríš v reinkarnáciu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:18.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenechávaj ma samu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úroveň vlny citov stúpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:37.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že mýtické beštie absorbujú negatívne city-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:44.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,závisť, úzkosť a strach - ako energiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Závisť?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai bude teraz moc riskantný!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako Aquarion, ich negatívne pocity budú zosilnené.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ich to zničí, tak je to ich hranica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem hlava!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinkarnácia je nezmysel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale som lepšie oblečený na Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neberiem rozkazy od nikoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:45.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty psisko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo do-?! Neverím tomu! To je absurdné!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň s tým!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukazovateľ Gattai vyletel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukazovateľ zjednotenia je v červenej zóne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Touto rýchlosťou, implodujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav to, Sirius! Spamätaj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj hlas sa k nemu nedostane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nádhera, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zahanbení svojou ohavnosťou,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,sú bezkrídlí predurčení, aby sa sami zničili.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A to ti nevadí?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:29.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Takéto chceš Slnečné Krídlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:34.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Otoha, je to tvoje prianie? Alebo žiarliš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:43.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Očisti sa od temných myšlienok
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:50.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a daj svoj šperk do môjho chrámu a modli sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekračujú štrukturálnu integritu obmedzenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:00.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion sa rozpadne!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám to! Šíp z môjho srdca...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:11.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosiahne ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:23.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:39.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius, nenechaj sa oklamať svetlom mýtických beštií!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika! Znova si prišla robiť problémy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neprerušuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:53.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to škaredý pohľad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nádherné svetlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:04.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravil som šperk zo svetla mýtických beštií?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:10.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď ľudia nájdu kúsok seba v iných,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:12.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak sa naučia milovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale keď si uvedomia, že nikdy nemôžu mať ten kus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak sa naučia žiarliť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:25.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiarlivosť je hlas, ktorý volá po tom kúsku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:27.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to energia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiarlivosť je energia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiarlivosť je energia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:39.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nos to so sebou a ži, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som hlava!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:51.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som Slnečné Krídlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je sila žiarlivosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:58.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme to so sebou nosiť a žiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cez cestu plnú tŕnia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:10.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty bastard! Chceš zo mňa kus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:18.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3. aura citov ukazuje nízky tlak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Citová aura vytvára búrku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:36.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion maximalizuje reakčný kvantum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neuveriteľné.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiarlivosť, daj nám silu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealotopia Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion to zvládol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvládli to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyhrali sme...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:24.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to ako ruža z kameňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako ruža.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvládli sme to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:37.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Znova nás porazil...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:40.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje Slnečné Krídlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:46.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale semienko bolo zasiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Malé semiačko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:52.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, krásna ruža sa chystá kvitnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje lístky prekypujú červenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje listy pružné a zelené.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:22:00.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoja lesklá, vlhká vôňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:03.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Príjmi moju krv tvojimi perami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:06.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochutnaj jazykom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:10.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhas smäd predtým než umrieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:16.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom kvitni... s deštrukciou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:17.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvitni.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:03.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, ako ste sa cítili 1. krát?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, myslíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:07.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme, Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:07.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:09.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "Prvý Gattai."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:43.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(464,407)}"Prvý Gattai"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:13.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neverím, že je to až také dobré...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:15.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
